{"type":"message","id":"678181b5","parentId":"e8fe5c9f","timestamp":"2026-02-28T07:29:11.056Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to specify the path parameter. Let me retry with the correct parameter name.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# AI-Powered Construction Intelligence Platform\n## UX/UI Design Documentation\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Executive Summary\n\nแพลตฟอร์มวิเคราะห์ข้อมูลก่อสร้างด้วย AI สำหรับผู้บริหารระดับสูงที่ต้องการ insights แบบ real-time โดยไม่ต้องเจอกับ Excel ที่ซับซ้อน\n\n**Key Design Principles:**\n- 👁️ **Glanceable**: ข้อมูลสำคัญเห็นใน 3 วินาที\n- 🎯 **Action-Oriented**: แนะนำการกระทำที่ชัดเจน\n- 🌍 **Context-Aware**: ปรับตามบทบาทผู้ใช้\n- 📱 **Anywhere Access**: ทำงานได้ทั้งบน desktop และมือถือที่ไซต์งาน\n\n---\n\n## 👥 User Personas\n\n### 1. CEO/COO (The Decision Maker)\n```\nGoals: ROI, Risk Management, Strategic Decisions\nPain Points: Too much data, no time, hates Excel\nNeeds: High-level overview, red flags, forecasts\nDevice: iPad Pro, iPhone (นอกสถานที่)\n```\n\n### 2. Project Manager (The Operator)\n```\nGoals: On-time delivery, Budget control\nPain Points: Multiple projects, resource allocation\nNeeds: Project status, alerts, team performance\nDevice: Laptop (ออฟฟิศ), Tablet (ไซต์งาน)\n```\n\n### 3. HR/ESG Officer (The Compliance Guardian)\n```\nGoals: Compliance, Employee wellbeing, Sustainability\nPain Points: Data scattered, reporting requirements\nNeeds: ESG metrics, workforce analytics, carbon tracking\nDevice: Desktop (ออฟฟิศ)\n```\n\n### 4. Investor (The Observer)\n```\nGoals: Portfolio performance, Risk assessment\nPain Points: Need quick overview, transparency\nNeeds: Financial health, ESG scores, forecasts\nDevice: Mobile (ดูระหว่างเดินทาง)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 Design System\n\n### Color Palette\n\n#### Primary Colors\n```css\n--primary-900: #0F172A;    /* Deep Navy - Primary text */\n--primary-800: #1E293B;    /* Slate 800 - Headers */\n--primary-700: #334155;    /* Slate 700 - Secondary text */\n--primary-600: #475569;    /* Slate 600 - Muted text */\n--primary-500: #64748B;    /* Slate 500 - Borders */\n--primary-400: #94A3B8;    /* Slate 400 - Disabled */\n--primary-300: #CBD5E1;    /* Slate 300 - Light borders */\n--primary-200: #E2E8F0;    /* Slate 200 - Backgrounds */\n--primary-100: #F1F5F9;    /* Slate 100 - Light BG */\n--primary-50:  #F8FAFC;    /* Slate 50 - Page BG */\n```\n\n#### Accent Colors (AI/Tech Feel)\n```css\n--accent-600: #2563EB;     /* Electric Blue - Primary actions */\n--accent-500: #3B82F6;     /* Blue 500 - Links */\n--accent-400: #60A5FA;     /* Blue 400 - Hover states */\n--accent-300: #93C5FD;     /* Blue 300 - Light accents */\n--accent-50:  #EFF6FF;     /* Blue 50 - Light backgrounds */\n```\n\n#### Semantic Colors (Traffic Light System)\n```css\n/* Status Colors - High Contrast */\n--status-success: #10B981;      /* Emerald 500 - On track */\n--status-success-bg: #D1FAE5;   /* Light green bg */\n--status-warning: #F59E0B;      /* Amber 500 - At risk */\n--status-warning-bg: #FEF3C7;   /* Light amber bg */\n--status-danger: #EF4444;       /* Red 500 - Critical */\n--status-danger-bg: #FEE2E2;    /* Light red bg */\n--status-info: #06B6D4;         /* Cyan 500 - Info */\n--status-info-bg: #CFFAFE;      /* Light cyan bg */\n```\n\n#### Data Visualization Colors\n```css\n--chart-blue: #3B82F6;\n--chart-purple: #8B5CF6;\n--chart-teal: #14B8A6;\n--chart-orange: #F97316;\n--chart-pink: #EC4899;\n```\n\n#### Dark Mode Colors\n```css\n--dark-bg-primary: #0F172A;     /* Page background */\n--dark-bg-secondary: #1E293B;   /* Card background */\n--dark-bg-tertiary: #334155;    /* Input backgrounds */\n--dark-text-primary: #F8FAFC;   /* Primary text */\n--dark-text-secondary: #94A3B8; /* Secondary text */\n--dark-border: #334155;         /* Borders */\n```\n\n### Typography\n\n#### Font Stack\n```css\n/* Thai + English Support */\n--font-display: 'Inter', 'Sarabun', -apple-system, sans-serif;\n--font-body: 'Inter', 'Sarabun', -apple-system, sans-serif;\n--font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Sarabun', monospace;\n```\n\n#### Type Scale\n```\nDisplay XL: 48px/56px - Bold (CEO headlines)\nDisplay L: 36px/44px - Bold (Page titles)\nDisplay M: 28px/36px - SemiBold (Section headers)\nDisplay S: 24px/32px - SemiBold (Card titles)\n\nHeading L: 20px/28px - SemiBold (Subsection)\nHeading M: 18px/26px - Medium (Card headers)\nHeading S: 16px/24px - Medium (Labels)\n\nBody L: 16px/24px - Regular (Primary text)\nBody M: 14px/22px - Regular (Secondary text)\nBody S: 12px/18px - Regular (Captions)\n\nData XL: 48px/56px - Bold (KPI numbers)\nData L: 32px/40px - Bold (Large metrics)\nData M: 24px/32px - SemiBold (Medium metrics)\nData S: 18px/26px - SemiBold (Small metrics)\n```\n\n### Spacing System\n```css\n--space-1: 4px;\n--space-2: 8px;\n--space-3: 12px;\n--space-4: 16px;\n--space-5: 20px;\n--space-6: 24px;\n--space-8: 32px;\n--space-10: 40px;\n--space-12: 48px;\n--space-16: 64px;\n```\n\n### Border Radius\n```css\n--radius-sm: 6px;    /* Inputs, small elements */\n--radius-md: 8px;    /* Cards, buttons */\n--radius-lg: 12px;   /* Large cards, modals */\n--radius-xl: 16px;   /* Featured sections */\n--radius-full: 9999px; /* Pills, avatars */\n```\n\n### Shadows\n```css\n--shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n--shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n--shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n--shadow-xl: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n--shadow-glow: 0 0 20px rgba(59,130,246,0.3); /* AI glow effect */\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Component Library\n\n### 1. Traffic Light Status System\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  🚦 PROJECT HEALTH DASHBOARD            │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                         │\n│  ┌─────────────┐ ┌─────────────┐       │\n│  │ 🟢 ON TRACK │ │ 🟡 AT RISK  │       │\n│  │    12       │ │     3       │       │\n│  │  Projects   │ │  Projects   │       │\n│  └─────────────┘ └─────────────┘       │\n│                                         │\n│  ┌─────────────┐ ┌─────────────┐       │\n│  │ 🔴 CRITICAL │ │ 📊 TOTAL    │       │\n│  │     1       │ │    16       │       │\n│  │  Project    │ │  Projects   │       │\n│  └─────────────┘ └─────────────┘       │\n│                                         │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Traffic Light Indicator Component:**\n```\nSizes: sm (8px), md (12px), lg (16px), xl (24px)\n\nStates:\n🟢 On Track: #10B981 - Solid fill\n🟡 At Risk: #F59E0B - Solid fill  \n🔴 Critical: #EF4444 - Pulsing animation\n⚪ On Hold: #94A3B8 - Dashed border\n🔵 Completed: #3B82F6 - Checkmark icon\n```\n\n### 2. Predictive Graph Component\n\n```\n┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  📈 AI FORECAST - Profit Projection              ✕ │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  Actual ───────  Forecast ─ - - -  Confidence     │\n│                                                    │\n│  ฿500M ┤                                    ╭─     │\n│        │                              ╭────╯      │\n│  ฿400M ┤                        ╭────╯             │\n│        │                  ╭────╯                   │\n│  ฿300M ┤    ╭────╭────╭──╯                        │\n│        │╭───╯                              ━━━━━   │\n│  ฿200M ┤━━━Actual━━━━━     ═════Forecast═════     │\n│        │                                           │\n│  ฿100M ┤                                    ▓▓▓▓▓  │\n│        │  ▓▓▓Actual▓▓▓    ·····95% CI·····  ▓▓▓▓▓  │\n│    ฿0M ┼────────────────────────────────────────   │\n│        Jan  Feb  Mar  Apr  May  Jun  Jul  Aug     │\n│                                                    │\n│  🎯 Accuracy: 95.2%  │  🔄 Last updated: 2m ago   │\n└────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Features:**\n- Gradient fill under actual line\n- Dashed line for forecast with confidence interval (shaded area)\n- Interactive tooltips\n- Pinch-to-zoom on mobile\n- Real-time update indicator\n\n### 3. Impact Score Card\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  IMPACT SCORE                ⓘ     │\n├──────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                      │\n│     ╭──────────────────╮             │\n│    ╱   ★★★★☆           ╲            │\n│   │      8.7             │           │\n│   │    EXCELLENT         │           │\n│    ╲   ─────────────   ╱            │\n│     ╰──────────────────╯             │\n│                                      │\n│  ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐          │\n│  │ 👥 85    │ │ 🌱 92    │          │\n│  │Employee  │ │ESG Score │          │\n│  │Satisfaction│ │         │          │\n│  └──────────┘ └──────────┘          │\n│                                      │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Scoring Display:**\n- Circular progress indicator\n- Star rating for quick scan\n- Breakdown pills for sub-scores\n- Color coding: 0-4 (🔴), 5-6 (🟡), 7-8 (🟢), 9-10 (🟢✨)\n\n### 4. ESG Dashboard Cards\n\n```\n┌───────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  🌍 ESG OVERVIEW                    🌓   │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                           │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐        │\n│  │  🌱 CARBON  │  │  😊 HAPPY   │        │\n│  │             │  │             │        │\n│  │  -24%       │  │   8.5/10    │        │\n│  │  vs last yr │  │  ↑ 0.3      │        │\n│  │  ████████░░ │  │  ████████▓░ │        │\n│  │  240 tCO2e  │  │  Top 10%    │        │\n│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘        │\n│                                           │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐        │\n│  │  ⚖️ GOV     │  │  🎯 SUSTAIN │        │\n│  │             │  │             │        │\n│  │   95%       │  │   A+        │        │\n│  │  Compliant  │  │   Rating    │        │\n│  │  █████████░ │  │  SET Index  │        │\n│  │  0 issues   │  │  Listed     │        │\n│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘        │\n│                                           │\n│  🏆 Carbon Credits Available: 120        │\n│  💰 Est. Value: ฿360,000                 │\n│                                           │\n└───────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 5. AI Trends Component\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  🤖 AI INSIGHTS                        🔔   │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                              │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │ 📊 FORECASTING                         │  │\n│  │ ─────────────────────────────────────  │  │\n│  │ • Q3 profit predicted: ฿450M (+12%)   │  │\n│  │ • Material costs trending up 8%       │  │\n│  │ [View Full Report →]                   │  │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│                                              │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │ ⚡ GENERATIVE SCHEDULING               │  │\n│  │ ─────────────────────────────────────  │  │\n│  │ ✓ Optimized 5 project schedules       │  │\n│  │ ✓ Saved 120 worker-hours this week    │  │\n│  │ [Apply Recommendations]                │  │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│                                              │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │ 👁️ COMPUTER VISION SAFETY              │  │\n│  │ ─────────────────────────────────────  │  │\n│  │ ⚠️ 3 safety alerts detected today      │  │\n│  │ 📍 Site: สุขุมวิท 64, รามคำแหง 42      │  │\n│  │ [View Live Feed →]                     │  │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│                                              │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📱 Wireframes\n\n### Page 1: Executive Dashboard (CEO View)\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 🔷 CONSTRUCTAI                                    [🌓] [👤] [⚙️] │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                 │\n│  👋 สวัสดี, คุณสมชาย  |  บริษัท สร้างสรรค์ก่อสร้าง จำกัด (มหาชน)   │\n│  Last updated: 2 minutes ago                    [📅 Q1 2026]    │\n│                                                                 │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                 │\n│  🚦 OVERALL PORTFOLIO HEALTH                                    │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │  🟢 12    🟡 3    🔴 1    ⚪ 0                          │   │\n│  │  On Track At Risk Critical On Hold                     │   │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌────────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐               │\n│  │  💰 TOTAL REVENUE  │  │  📈 PROJECTED Q1   │               │\n│  │                    │  │                    │               │\n│  │   ฿1.2 Billion     │  │    ฿1.45B          │               │\n│  │   ↑ 15% vs last yr │  │   🎯 95% accuracy  │               │\n│  │                    │  │   [View Forecast →]│               │\n│  └────────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘               │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │  📊 REVENUE FORECAST (AI-Powered)                       │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  │    ฿M │    ╭────╮                                    │   │\n│  │  1.5M │   ╱      ╲    ════════════════════           │   │\n│  │  1.0M │  ╱        ╲___/                               │   │\n│  │  0.5M │ ╱  Actual  ╲···· Forecast ···· 95% CI          │   │\n│  │    0M ┼─────────────────────────────────────          │   │\n│  │       Jan  Feb  Mar  Apr  May  Jun                    │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌────────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐               │\n│  │  🌍 ESG SCORE      │  │  ⚡ IMPACT SCORE   │               │\n│  │                    │  │                    │               │\n│  │     ⭐ 8.7         │  │     ⭐ 8.5         │               │\n│  │    EXCELLENT       │  │    EXCELLENT       │               │\n│  │  Top 15% SET       │  │  ↑ 0.3 this month  │               │\n│  │  [View Details →]  │  │  [View Details →]  │               │\n│  └────────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘               │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │  🚨 ATTENTION REQUIRED                                  │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  │  🔴 Project: สุขุมวิท 64 - Budget overrun risk (87%)      │   │\n│  │     [View Details]  [Schedule Meeting]  [Reallocate]    │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  │  🟡 Project: รามคำแหง 42 - Delay risk (65%)             │   │\n│  │     [View Details]  [Review Timeline]                   │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │  🤖 AI INSIGHTS                                         │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  │  💡 Material costs trending up 12% - Consider bulk      │   │\n│  │     purchasing for Q2 projects                          │   │\n│  │     [Apply Strategy]  [Dismiss]                         │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  │  ⚡ Workforce optimization opportunity: Redeploy 15      │   │\n│  │     workers from Site A to Site B                       │   │\n│  │     [View Recommendation]                               │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                                                 │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Page 2: Project Detail View\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ ← โครงการสุขุมวิท 64                              [🌓] [👤]     │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                 │\n│  🏗️ โครงการสุขุมวิท 64 - คอนโดมิเนียมหรู 45 ชั้น              │\n│  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ 68% Complete           │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │  STATUS: 🔴 CRITICAL - Budget Risk Detected             │   │\n│  │  Next Milestone: Topping off ceremony in 12 days        │   │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                                                 │\n│  [Overview] [Financials] [Schedule] [ESG] [Safety] [Team]      │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌──────────────┐ ┌──────────────┐ ┌──────────────┐          │\n│  │   BUDGET     │  │   TIMELINE   │  │   QUALITY    │          │\n│  │              │  │              │  │              │          │\n│  │   🟡 87%     │  │   🟢 92%     │  │   🟢 95%     │          │\n│  │   ฿450M/520M │  │   On Track   │  │   Excellent  │          │\n│  │   Risk: High │  │   12 days ahead│ │   0 defects  │          │\n│  └──────────────┘ └──────────────┘ └──────────────┘          │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │  💰 FINANCIAL HEALTH                                    │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  │  Budget Utilization    │  Cost Forecast                │   │\n│  │  ████████████████░░ 87%│  ─────────────────────────    │   │\n│  │                        │  Projected: ฿510M (+2%)        │   │\n│  │  Committed: ฿450M      │  Confidence: 89%              │   │\n│  │  Spent: ฿380M          │  Risk: 🔴 High                │   │\n│  │  Remaining: ฿70M       │                               │   │\n│  │                        │  [View Detailed Breakdown]    │   │\n│  │                        │                               │   │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │  📅 PROJECT TIMELINE                                    │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  │  Foundation  Structure   MEP     Finishing  Handover   │   │\n│  │  ✓✓✓✓✓✓    ✓✓✓✓✓○○   ○○○○○○   ○○○○○○○○   ○○○○○○○○    │   │\n│  │  Complete    85%        0%       0%        0%          │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  │  🎯 Critical Path: Structure completion by Mar 15      │   │\n│  │  ⚠️  Risk: Material delivery delay (Steel beams)       │   │\n│  │                                                         │   │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌────────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐               │\n│  │  👥 TEAM (45)      │  │  🌍 ESG METRICS    │               │\n│  │                    │  │                    │