low 3: ESG Officer Reporting\n```\nDashboard → ESG Dashboard\n                ↓\n    Review 3 Pillars (Env + Social + Gov)\n                n    Check Carbon Credits\n                ↓\n    Download Full Report\n                ↓\n    Submit to SET / Investors\n```\n\n#### Flow 4: Site Visit (Mobile)\n```\nOpen Mobile App → Quick Portfolio View\n                ↓\n    Select Project at Site\n                ↓\n    View Safety Dashboard (Live Cameras)\n                ↓\n    Check Team Status\n                ↓\n    Record Voice Note / Photo\n                ↓\n    Sync when Online\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📐 Responsive Breakpoints\n\n```\nDesktop XL:  1440px+  (CEO Workstation)\nDesktop:     1024px+  (Standard Laptop)\nTablet:      768px    (iPad - Site Office)\nMobile:      375px    (iPhone - Field Use)\n```\n\n### Breakpoint Behavior\n\n| Component | Desktop | Tablet | Mobile |\n|-----------|---------|--------|--------|\n| Navigation | Horizontal tabs | Collapsible | Bottom nav |\n| Dashboard Grid | 4 columns | 2 columns | 1 column |\n| Charts | Full interactive | Simplified | Sparklines |\n| Cards | Side by side | Stacked | Stacked |\n| Tables | Full data | Key cols | Cards view |\n| AI Insights | Sidebar | Inline | Accordion |\n\n### Mobile-First Considerations\n\n1. **Touch Targets**: Minimum 44x44px\n2. **Swipe Gestures**: Chart zoom, tab switching\n3. **Offline Mode**: Cache critical data\n4. **Voice Input**: Notes and search\n5. **Camera Integration**: Safety reports\n6. **GPS**: Auto-detect site location\n\n---\n\n## 🌓 Dark Mode Implementation\n\n### When to Use\n- Site visits (reduce glare)\n- Evening work (reduce eye strain)\n- Low-light environments\n- User preference\n\n### Toggle Location\n- Header (always visible)\n- System preference sync\n- Per-device memory\n\n### Color Mapping\n```\nLight → Dark\n#FFFFFF → #0"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,